Look for the user in the output. For example:
jenkins   1234  0.0  0.1 123456 7890 ?        Ssl  12:34   0:00 /usr/bin/java -jar /usr/share/jenkins/jenkins.war
In this case, Jenkins is running as the jenkins user.

